+    {
+        // The companion's map-open (AddUiMode windows={'Map'}) enters GM_Inventory, but the mode
+        // is opened via a DEFERRED Lua action, so it is not open yet when CMP:openmap is drained.
+        // The caller polls this every frame until it returns true. Return false while GM_Inventory
